Privacy Policy
Effective date:
3 June 2024
AIRGSM PTE. LTD., doing business as Airalo (
www.AIRALO.com
) (“Airalo,” “we,” “us,” or “our”), recognizes the importance of your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, share and protect your personal information, also known as personal data. This Privacy Policy also tells you about your rights and choices with respect to your personal information, and how you can reach us to get answers to your questions.
By registering an account or otherwise using or visiting any Airalo website, application, product, software, tool, data feed, and/or service (collectively the “Service”), you understand and agree to the terms of this policy.
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, retain, and protect your personal information. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully.
