California Sensitive Information Disclosure.
We collect the following categories of sensitive personal information (as defined under California law): biometric information, geolocation, social security number or other government issued ID information, account log-in, payment information. This information is collected in order to process transactions, comply with laws, manage our business, or provide you with services. Note that we do not use such information for any purposes that are not identified within the California Privacy Rights Act Section 1798.121.
